          "Code": "local player = _UserService.LocalPlayer\n\n-- 주인이 아닐 경우 --------\nif player.Name ~= self.MapInfo.MapOwnerName then\n\treturn\nend\n\nif player.PlayerMove.ClickedEntity == self.Entity then\n\tself:IsHold()\nend",
